# Day 3 â€“ Pivot Table Analysis

## Objective
To analyze disease-wise and department-wise performance using pivot tables.

## Analysis Performed

### Pivot 1: Disease-wise Analysis
- Total patients per disease
- Total profit generated per disease

### Pivot 2: Department-wise Analysis
- Average length of stay per department
- Total revenue per department

## Tools Used
- Microsoft Excel Pivot Tables

## Outcome
Identified high-profit diseases and departments with longer patient stays.
